title: Population and Housing Statistics by Province; Total/Urban/Rural, Region Metropolitana de Santiago, Chile, 2002
name: Population and Housing Statistics by Province; Total/Urban/Rural, Region Metropolitana de Santiago, Chile, 2002
description:
This data displays statistics on population and housing by by Province in the Region of Metropolitana de Santiago of Chile in 2002. It is divided into the 3 types of total, urban, and rural.

The data comes from the Instituto Nacional de Estadísticas of Chile in their 2007 DIVISIÓN POLÍTICO-ADMINISTRATIVA Y CENSAL Report.

The data includes for each province: total population 2002, total population 2002, urban population 2002, rural population 2002, total housing 2002, urban housing 2002, rural housing 2002, commune area in Km2, province ID, and province name.

author.source: Instituto Nacional de Estadísticas of Chile
